\c 16
\s Hagari naIshimaeri
\p
\v 1 Zvino Sarai mukadzi waAbhuramu waiva asingamuberekeri\x + 15.2,3.\x* uye waiva nemurandakadzi, muEgipita\x + 12.16; 21.9.\x*, uye zita rake raiva Hagari\x + VaGar. 4.24.\x*.
\v 2 Sarai\x + 20.3,9.\x* ndokuti kuna Abhuramu: Tarira hako, Jehovha wakandidzivisa kubereka\x + 20.18; 30.2. 1 Sam. 1.5,6.\x*; pinda hako kumurandakadzi wangu; zvimwe ndingavakwa naye. Abhuramu ndokuteerera kuinzwi raSarai.
\v 3 Zvino Sarai mukadzi waAbhuramu wakatora Hagari muEgipita murandakadzi wake, pakupera kwemakore gumi Abhuramu agere panyika yeKenani\x + 12.5.\x*, ndokumupa kuna Abhuramu murume wake kuva mukadzi kwaari.
\v 4 Zvino wakapinda kuna Hagari, iye ndokubata mimba. Zvino wakati aona kuti wabata mimba, vatenzikadzi vake vakashoreka pameso ake\x + Zvir. 30.21,23.\x*.
\v 5 Sarai ndokuti kuna Abhuramu: Kukanganiswa kwangu kuri pamusoro pako. Ini ndakapa murandakadzi wangu pachipfuva chako, zvino waona kuti wabata mimba, ndinoshoreka pameso ake. Jehovha ngaatonge pakati pangu newe\x + 31.53. 1 Sam. 24.12.\x*.
\v 6 Abhuramu ndokuti kuna Sarai: Tarira, murandakadzi wako \add uri\add* paruoko rwako\x + Job. 2.6. Jer. 38.5.\x*. Muitire zvakanaka pameso ako. Zvino Sarai wakamubata zvakaipa, iye ndokutiza pachiso chake\x + Eki. 2.15.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Mutumwa waJehovha ndokumuwana pachitubu chemvura murenje\x + 20.1. Eki. 15.22. 1 Sam. 15.7.\x*, pachitubu panzira yeShuri\x + 25.18; Eki. 15.22.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino wakati: Hagari, murandakadzi waSarai, unobvepi, uye unoendepi? Iye ndokuti: Ndinotiza pachiso chaSarai vatenzikadzi vangu.
\v 9 Mutumwa waJehovha ndokuti kwaari: Dzokera kuna vatenzikadzi vako, ugozvininipisa pasi pemaoko avo.
\v 10 Mutumwa waJehovha ndokuti kwaari: Ndichawanza zvikuru chizvarwa chako\x + 17.20; 21.18; 25.12-18.\x* kuti chisaverengwa nekuwanda.
\v 11 Mutumwa waJehovha ndokuti kwaari: Tarira, une mimba, uye uchabereka mwanakomana, uye uchatumidza zita rake\x + 17.19. Mat. 1.21. Ruk. 1.13,31.\x* Ishimaeri, nokuti Jehovha wanzwa kutambudzika kwako.
\v 12 Iyewo achava munhu ari mbongoro yemusango\x + 21.20.\x*; ruoko rwake rwucharwisa vose, neruoko rwevose rwuchamurwisa; uye achagara pamberi pechiso chehama dzake dzese\x + 25.18.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino akatumidza zita raJehovha wakataurirana naye \add kuti\add*: Imwi Mwari wekuona. Nokuti wakati: Pano neni ndamutarisa here iye unondiona?
\v 14 Naizvozvo chitubu chakanzi Bheeri-Rahai-Royi\x + 24.62; 25.11.\x*; tarira, chiri pakati peKadheshi\x + Num. 13.26. 14.7; 20.1.\x* neBheredhi.
\v 15 Hagari ndokuberekera Abhuramu mwanakomana; Abhuramu ndokutumidza zita remwanakomana wake, Hagari waamukabereka: Ishimaeri\x + 16.11.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino Abhuramu waiva wemakore makumi masere nematanhatu Hagari paakaberekera Abhuramu Ishimaeri.